-I don't mind.

06:25.586 --> 06:27.120
-Really, it's, uh, it's okay.
-No, no.

06:27.154 --> 06:29.590
It's no problem.
I'd be killing time, you know?

06:32.059 --> 06:36.930
Um... look, I just, uh,

06:36.964 --> 06:41.401
I, um, I don't want
this really nice,

06:41.435 --> 06:46.807
