-I am. I'm not ashamed of it.

07:02.322 --> 07:04.492
-You'll see. Oh, no, you'll see.
-Of course you are.

07:04.525 --> 07:06.527
Okay.

07:08.929 --> 07:11.665
Mm

07:11.699 --> 07:14.134
It's my co-op kitchen proposal.

07:14.167 --> 07:15.469
