07:15.503 --> 07:17.270
No, keep it on.

07:17.304 --> 07:19.239
I like you a little slim thick.

07:19.272 --> 07:22.009
BETH:
Mm-- oh, that feels good.

07:22.042 --> 07:24.011
-Do not stop.
-Okay.

07:24.044 --> 07:25.846
Just don't keep doing that thing

07:25.879 --> 07:27.481
where you're directing me
the entire time.

07:27.515 --> 07:29.983
Ooh, just a little bit higher.

07:30.017 --> 07:32.019
Oh-- I mean, uh, no.

07:32.052 --> 07:33.020
-I'll shut up.
-Uh-huh.

07:33.053 --> 07:34.454
Please don't stop.

07:34.488 --> 07:36.624
This proposal
is kicking my ass, babe.

07:36.657 --> 07:38.492
Oh, and I may have
to go into work tomorrow

07:38.526 --> 07:39.760
