07:39.793 --> 07:41.428
-Yep.

07:41.461 --> 07:43.831
Just a little
bit lower, more pressure.

07:43.864 --> 07:46.934
I think I'll take Deja to
the rec center by our building.

07:46.967 --> 07:48.168
