more comfortable there.

07:57.811 --> 07:59.379
-Couldn't hurt-- ow.
-Sorry. That's...

07:59.412 --> 08:01.114
but you-you said more pressure.

08:01.148 --> 08:03.350
-Yeah, but modulate, baby.
-Right. You got it.

08:03.383 --> 08:05.285
Modulate, but don't stop.

08:08.656 --> 08:11.058
