to my family.

09:11.151 --> 09:12.853
Yeah, I guess you're right.

09:12.886 --> 09:16.857
Some things are best kept
between a husband and his wife

09:16.890 --> 09:18.091
and his Lyft driver.

09:18.125 --> 09:20.527
