for you guys.

09:20.560 --> 09:22.462
-Okay, thanks.
-Thanks.

09:44.117 --> 09:46.253
Looks like you could use a hand.

09:46.286 --> 09:48.455
Thank you. I can manage.

09:48.488 --> 09:50.090
Fair enough.

09:52.192 --> 09:54.962
Please, do not touch my things.
I said I can manage.

09:57.765 --> 10:00.100
WILLIAM:
I didn't catch your name.

10:00.133 --> 10:02.002
RANDALL:
Hey, ChiChi.

10:02.035 --> 10:04.237
Hey, Randall.
Is everything okay?

10:04.271 --> 10:06.840
-I did. Everything's good.

10:06.874 --> 10:09.276
I just, uh, I wanted
to introduce Deja to Sky.

10:11.011 --> 10:12.412
CHICHI:
Sky, over here.

10:12.445 --> 10:14.682
RANDALL:
Hey, Sky. This is Deja.

10:14.715 --> 10:15.983
Deja, Sky.

10:16.016 --> 10:18.251
-Hey.
-Hi.

10:18.285 --> 10:19.853
