Hi, um, uh, this message
is for the admissions office.

40:42.474 --> 40:45.443
I'm Randall Pearson,
and I already sent in my form

40:45.477 --> 40:47.178
saying that I'll be
attending Howard this fall,

40:47.212 --> 40:49.748
but I just wanted to call
to say that, actually,

40:49.781 --> 40:52.984
I... actually, I won't be.

40:53.018 --> 40:58.356
I got to, uh, stay,
stay close to home for family.

41:00.225 --> 41:03.194
Thank you for this opportunity.

41:11.002 --> 41:12.270
-KEVIN: Hi.
-Ah.

41:12.303 --> 41:14.039
-My brother, on the big screen.
-Hi.

41:14.072 --> 41:15.140
Damn.

41:15.173 --> 41:17.108
Is this movie gonna make me cry?

41:17.142 --> 41:18.844
Uh, well, you cry
at everything, so probably.

41:18.877 --> 41:20.946
Oh, it's gonna make me
cry buckets, I can tell.

41:22.914 --> 41:24.482
Uh...
-Yeah.

41:24.516 --> 41:25.884
You missed quite
a bit, actually.

41:25.917 --> 41:27.052
Um, Kate and Toby are doing IVF.

41:27.085 --> 41:28.520
-Yeah.

41:28.554 --> 41:30.288
-RANDALL: Good for them.
-I think so. Yeah.

41:30.321 --> 41:32.023
KEVIN: Mom kind of flipped out
a little bit, though.

41:32.057 --> 41:33.825
You know, which upset Kate.
She was like,

41:33.859 --> 41:35.961
"Well, I'm the only one
that's gonna be able to pass on

41:35.994 --> 41:37.996
a piece of Dad," right,
which made me upset, and--

41:38.029 --> 41:40.498
even though, to be honest with
you, it really wasn't about that

41:40.532 --> 41:42.233
for me, you know
what I mean? You...

41:42.267 --> 41:44.670
Let me ask you a question.

41:44.703 --> 41:48.774
Do you think serious people
take me seriously?

41:51.677 --> 41:53.645
What? Hey.

41:53.679 --> 41:57.082
No, I... She said
she was the only one

41:57.115 --> 41:59.217
who could pass on
a piece of Dad?

